{"tid":428102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投]一句講晒，你支唔支持獨立？","createTime":"2017-10-07T20:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T01:46:47.000Z","uid":132859,"like":65,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"590a13c51a058f4c5aa3c9cc15c969b24a009daf","tid":428102,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T20:08:30.000Z","msg":"你是否贊成香港人應有自己的獨立民族國家？<br />\n正皮=支持<br />\n負皮=反對<br />\nDo you think that Hong Kong citizens deserve to have their own independent nation state?<br />\nUpvote for Yes<br />\nDownvote for No"},{"pid":"b14749e02007520eed830f704d65150bf8c258fc","tid":428102,"uid":86378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T20:09:58.000Z","msg":"當然<br />\nOf course"},{"pid":"8b4bc59f3cb88d37b73ad964b079ee24dfce36de","tid":428102,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:06:30.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fecc0ecc5c8e68696ed882b9cd594b1dab2e5818","tid":428102,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:46:16.000Z","msg":"打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6deceaf02668af325b936f04707be77cdb03474e","tid":428102,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T12:38:21.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0c262481b0204e7246a622404f46be5d7ea4ee9c","tid":428102,"uid":66559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:29:09.000Z","msg":"正經post冇人理<br />\n垃圾post幾千正評"},{"pid":"72c2bb6bc30a4ba3ed3d9c5e48ac3fcbe269e4e1","tid":428102,"uid":68803,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"反對：因為我係鍵國post留低左條問題成個禮拜都冇人識答。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題如下：<br />\n香港真係獨立左之後，我地可以憑嘜野keep住香港安全同埋經營落去先？<br />\n單講經濟：<br />\n1）獨立左既香港就唔再係一個轉口港，內地冇可能唔抵制/報復香港，限制貨物唔可以經香港轉口去內地。單睇2016年轉口貨物6成經內地，一但獨立令進出口貿易業收皮。<br />\n2）香港個市有唔少股都有中資背景，香港獨立後呢d資金&amp;公司就會撤走。香港資金流減少，香港到時仲有幾有資金對外貿易？<br />\n3）香港基本上大部份係第三級生產，當唔少公司撒資時候，大量工作人口失業，市民變得減少支出，服務行業飲食業等等必定減少，引發經濟衰退。申請社會援助人數大量增加，到時你地所重奪主權既政府支出大幅度增加，但因為經濟蕭條，稅收減少而令到政府機能停止。<br />\n<br />\n獨立當然唔單止引申咁少問題出黎，我只係舉出幾樣好實際既問題。<br />\n但基本上，當經濟衰落，社會保障就會收皮，更加唔洗提軍備同埋營運政府。<br />\n鍵國撚有冇方法solve獨立後所引申既問題先？<br />\n我只係想睇下鍵國撚叫人緊行既路係生路定死路姐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb0eaf97b5392214e021e2b3e6f0ab3266183fc","tid":428102,"uid":66559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T00:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6265d3bbf44ae18b510f179421c80c942c7880e4","tid":428102,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a36830b2616136e33c6ad39ac847defb21b44d5","tid":428102,"uid":66559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T01:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}